            <!-- Learn More Section -->
            <section class="container learn-more">
                <h2 class="homepage-title">Welcome to Baldwin Stables LLC</h2>
                <!-- <p class="homepage-subtext">"The essential joy of being with horses is that it brings us in contact with
                    the rare elements of grace, beauty, spirit
                    and freedom."</p> -->
                <div class="learn-more-container">
                    <div class="learn-more-card">
                        <div class="card-img card-img-one"></div>
                        <p class="card-title">About Us

                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">Though the Arabian horse is our passion, all breeds are welcome for
                            boarding
                            and/or
                            training. We currently have
                            arabians, half-arabians, quarter horses, paints, and morgans to name a few.
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn-link" href="/about"><button class="btn learn-more-button">Learn
                                More</button></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more-card">
                        <div class="card-img card-img-two"></div>
                        <p class="card-title">Our Facilities</p>
                        <p class="card-text">Baldwin Stables is located on seven fenced in wooded acres, in the quiet
                            Connecticut town of Deep River. Sporting an
                            indoor arena, outdoor ring, and bordering Cockaponsett State Forest (with miles of trail
                            access)
                            our
                            location is perfect
                            for the riding enthusiast. Whether you are looking for a structured lesson in a ring or a
                            leisurely
                            walk through nature,
                            we have it all.
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn-link" href="/boarding"><button class="btn learn-more-button">Learn
                                More</button></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="learn-more-card">
                        <div class="card-img card-img-three"></div>
                        <p class="card-title">Training</p>
                        <p class="card-text">In 2002, the dream of creating Baldwin Stables became a reality. Jack and
                            Karen
                            Baldwin purchased the facility and went
                            to work renovating and improving the property. Today, we proudly provide our clients with a
                            well
                            maintained and groomed
                            stable.
                        </p>
                        <a class="btn-link" href="/training"><button class="btn learn-more-button">Learn
                                More</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

